'We have tried several times to modify the toilet to make it more convenient but there really is not space to do very much, and we decided to leave it because it's better to have a facility that some people can use occasionally rather than nothing at all.

'The bottom line is that land is very scarce here in the district and our options are very limited.

'Because there are a lot of residential properties here in the area a lot of people walk past, and the toilet is in great demand even if it's not available to everyone.'

